modName: Heels on platform with stockings for CBBE 3_4f with Bodyslide for HDThighheels
summary:
For CBBE 3.4f
24 variants of heels, 13 variants of stockings, requires HDT high heels
descriptionHtml:
It is update of my old mod

24 variants of heels, 13 variants of stockings
Requires [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36213]HDT high heels[/url]
heels are following variants: black, bluefull , bluetop, cyanfull, cyantop, dark green full, dark green top, dark purp full, dark purp top, dark red full, dark red top, olive full, olive top, orange full, orange top, pink full, pink top, red, red full, red top, silver, white full, white top, yellow

stockings are following variants: transparent (black, cyan , olive, purple, red, white) net (black, blue, darkred, green, orange, pink, white)

for model thanks to DonMichael71 [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15982]High Heels for Modding[/url]
craftable in leather

This file is for CBBE 3.4f body, in optional available bodyslide file
File for CBBE 3.2, UNP and ADEC is [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/92180]here[/url]

Credits
for celtic brushes thanks to Falln-Stock  http://falln-stock.deviantart.com/art/Celtic-Knot-Brushes-92727098
